OL,5, In the US, new guidelines on how       
OL,6, paediatricians should treat childhood  
OL,7, obesity have been met with some        
OL,8, criticism.                             
OL,10,FThe American Academy of Paediatrics has
OL,11,Frecommended intensive therapy for      
OL,12,Fchildren as young as six and weight    
OL,13,Floss drugs and surgery for those in    
OL,14,Ftheir early teens.                     
OL,16,FBut some fear this approach will come  
OL,17,Fat the expense of a healthy and active 
OL,18,Flifestyle.                             
OL,20,FOne child in five is obese in the US.  
